ej.bluetooth

Class BluetoothDataTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • ej.bluetooth.BluetoothDataTypes

  • public class BluetoothDataTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    The BluetoothDataTypes class enumerates the values for advertising data types.

    Refer to «Core Specification Supplement Part A, 1 Data Types Definitions and Formats».
